data.description: LOOK NO FURTHER!!!! This home is nestled in a great location within the sought after Kings Grant subdivision. It is located just off King Grant's golf course, and is situated on a corner lot. This home boasts 4 Bedrooms, 3 Full Baths, a Cathedral Ceiling in the living room, a Formal Dining room, a screened in patio, and an upstairs Mother-in-law suite that is perfect for guest(s) during the holidays. Set your appointment, and make this house your home today
